ActImmigration and Refugee Protection Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Immigration and Refugee Protection Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the IMMIGRATION AND REFUGEE PROTECTION REGULATIONS in order to bring greater clarity, consistency and efficiency to the Ministerial relief application process, and to govern the overall application process only. These Regulations are not intended to affect decision-making factors.
